de-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-76.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade Talon 35th anniversary edition\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade Talon 35th anniversary edition\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"Pivot Switchblade Talon 35th anniversary edition\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-73.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade Talon 35th anniversary edition\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade Talon 35th anniversary edition\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n<figcaption>(Photos/Pivot/Jens Staudt)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But we can’t all have our own Sun Eagle Talon, so to pay homage to the original bike, Pivot is offering 300 limited-edition <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pivot-switchblade-2024-improved-suspension-updated-geometry/\" target=\"_blank\">Switchblades</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Available in Team and Pro Builds in both SRAM or Shimano and all with carbon wheels, the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10060&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brgcgearbikingpivotswitchblade&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backcountry.com%2Fpivot-switchblade-pro-x0-transmission-carbon-wheel-mountain-bike\">Talon 35th Anniversary bikes</a> carry a $200 premium over the standard build which works out to retail prices of $9,199 to $11,599. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-35th-anniversary-Sun-Eagle-Talon-hat-bottle-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>(Photo/Bikerumor)</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img /><figcaption>(Photo/Bikerumor)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img /><figcaption>(Photo/Bikerumor)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you miss out on one of those 300 bikes, or don’t want to spend the $10k, you can still get your Talon fix with a limited-edition hat and water bottle. If you want the matching hip pack and shades, you’ll have to get those straight from <a href=\"https://waveproducts.com/products/thruster-mtb-fanny-pack?variant=43551538282688\" target=\"_blank\">Wave</a> or <a href=\"https://www.pitviper.com/products/the-italo-try-hard\" target=\"_blank\">Pit Viper</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For more on the history of Pivot Cycles, <a href=\"https://www.pivotcycles.com/en/35-years-of-innovation-the-cocalis-chronicles/\" target=\"_blank\">this piece written by Richard Cunningham</a> is a must-read. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.pitviper.com\" target=\"_blank\">pivotcycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pink-switchblade-limited-edition-original-sun-eagle-talon-mtb/\">Pink Switchblade is a Limited Edition Homage to the Original Sun Eagle Talon</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d89658eac8b32fbb6614c6934746572cc87786384723d9835dc21a5287c7f5a9","category":"Cycling"}